items.sentence: I wonder whether Tom will go to Boston or not.
I wonder whether or not I should do that, too.
Tom wondered what it would be like to be deaf.
I know that you weren\'t the one who did that.
I know that you won\'t be in Boston next week.
I know that you\'re learning French at school.
Would you look after the place while I\'m out?
Tom didn\'t come and Mary didn\'t come either.
I fled to Australia to avoid getting arrested.
Perhaps that\'s something I can help you with.
